<L>__{exterior the desert (various shots) day}
<A>__{indy cuts cross country avoiding the road the convoy has taken. he leaps gullies, climbs dunes, slides down slopes. soon the convoy comes into view far below him. he tears along a parallel ridge, like an indian shadowing a wagon train.}
